column1: Changes in Producer Price Indexes, 2022 through 2025
Note: The most recent forecast was published on October 25, 2024. The next forecast will be published on November 25, 2024.
1. Forecasts are grouped in three columns by the lower-bound, midpoint, and upper-bound of the prediction interval.
2. Each cell represents the percent-change range for each point in the forecast.
Source: U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics Producer Price Indexes (not seasonally adjusted) and forecasts by USDA, Economic Research Service.
